                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The National Security Council Meeting of October 17, 1951, was devoted in part to
                    a discussion of military assistance. For an account of that meeting by Secretary
                    of State Acheson, see memorandum of conversation by Lucius D. Battle, Special
                    Assistant to the Secretary of State, October 18, page 242.</p>
            </div>
